_sText: This map is a treefort-based map with two levels for gameplay. There are ramps connecting the upper areas of the towers to the center fort and hedges and other brushwork for cover on the ground. Custom textures by {cDS} winnebago_warrior.  This is my first attempt at creating custom textures and I am aware that they are.....cheesy =).  thanks to {cDS} peanuts and {cDS} The Black Rose for tips and pointers along the design path.
